<!-- 定義與症狀 -->
'''冠狀動脈疾病'''（{{lang-en|coronary artery disease, CAD}}）又稱'''缺血性心臟病'''（{{lang-en|ischemic heart disease, IHD}}）<ref>{{cite book |last=Bhatia |first=Sujata K. |title=Biomaterials for clinical applications |year=2010 |publisher=Springer |location=New York |ISBN=9781441969200 |page=23 |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=bXtaX468LRYC&pg=PA23 |edition=Online-Ausg. |access-date=2015-03-29 |archive-date=2014-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102120950/http://books.google.ca/books?id=bXtaX468LRYC&pg=PA23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、'''冠狀動脈粥樣硬化心臟病'''<ref>{{cite web |title=Coronary heart disease - causes, symptoms, prevention |url=https://www.southerncross.co.nz/AboutTheGroup/HealthResources/MedicalLibrary/tabid/178/vw/1/ItemID/191/ |work=Southern Cross Healthcare Group |accessdate=15 September 2013 |archive-date=2016-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404040843/https://www.southerncross.co.nz/aboutthegroup/healthresources/medicallibrary/tabid/178/vw/1/itemid/191 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、'''冠狀動脈粥樣硬化心血管疾病'''（{{lang-en|coronary atherosclerotic heart disease, CAHD}}）<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Faxon |first1=D. P.|title=Atherosclerotic Vascular Disease Conference: Executive Summary: Atherosclerotic Vascular Disease Conference Proceeding for Healthcare Professionals From a Special Writing Group of the American Heart Association |journal=Circulation|date=1 June 2004|volume=109|issue=21|pages=2595–2604 |doi = 10.1161/01.CIR.0000128517.52533.DB}}</ref>和'''冠狀動脈心臟病'''（{{lang-en|coronary heart disease}}）<ref>{{cite web |title=Coronary heart disease |url=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/007115.htm |publisher=ADAM |accessdate=15 September 2013 |archive-date=2013-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130912095525/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/007115.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>（簡稱'''冠心病'''），涉及心臟動脈的斑塊堆積（[[動脈粥樣硬化|動脈粥樣硬化]]）導致流向心肌的血流降低。冠狀動脈疾病是最常見的[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]<ref name=GDB2013>{{cite journal |last1=GBD 2013 Mortality and Causes of Death |first1=Collaborators|title=Global, regional, and national age-sex specific all-cause and cause-specific mortality for 240 causes of death, 1990-2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013. |journal=Lancet |date=17 December 2014 |pmid=25530442 |doi = 10.1016/S0140-6736(14)61682-2}}</ref>。型態包含穩定型[[心絞痛|心絞痛]]、{{Link-en|非穩定型心絞痛|Unstable angina}}、[[心肌梗塞|心肌梗塞]]和[[猝死|猝死]]<ref name=Wong2014>{{cite journal |last1=Wong|first1=ND|title=Epidemiological studies of CHD and the evolution of preventive cardiology.|journal=Nature reviews. Cardiology|date=May 2014|volume=11|issue=5|pages=276-89 |pmid=24663092}}</ref>。常見的症狀包括[[胸痛|胸痛]]或不適，有時會轉移到肩膀、手臂、背部、頸部或下顎<ref name=HLB2014>{{cite web |title=What Are the Signs and Symptoms of Coronary Heart Disease? |url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/cad/signs |website=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/ |accessdate=23 February 2015 |date=September 29, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224034615/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/cad/signs |archive-date=2015-02-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。有些人可能會有[[胸口灼熱|胸口灼熱]]的感覺<ref name=HLB2014/>。通常症狀在運動或情緒壓力下出現，持續時間不超過數分鐘且休息會緩解<ref name=HLB2014/>。有時會伴隨[[呼吸困難|呼吸困難]]，有時則是毫無症狀<ref name=HLB2014/>。少數人以[[心肌梗塞|心肌梗塞]]為最初的表現<ref name=CDC2013>{{cite web |title=Coronary Artery Disease (CAD) |url=http://www.cdc.gov/heartdisease/coronary_ad.htm |website=cdc.gov |accessdate=23 February 2015 |date=March 12, 2013 |archive-date=2015-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150302152003/http://www.cdc.gov/heartdisease/coronary_ad.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他可能的併發症包含[[心臟衰竭|心臟衰竭]]或[[心律不整|心律不整]]<ref name=CDC2013/>。

<!--成因與診斷 -->
危險因子包括：[[高血壓|高血壓]]、[[吸菸|抽菸]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]、缺乏運動、[[肥胖症|肥胖]]、[[高胆固醇血症|血液中膽固醇含量過高]]、營養不良和酗[[乙醇|酒]]等<ref name=WHO2011>{{cite book|last1=Mendis|first1=Shanthi|last2=Puska,|first2=Pekka|last3=Norrving|first3=Bo|title=Global atlas on cardiovascular disease prevention and control|date=2011|publisher=World Health Organization in collaboration with the World Heart Federation and the World Stroke Organization|location=Geneva|ISBN=9789241564373|pages=3-18|edition=1st ed.|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2011/9789241564373_eng.pdf?ua=1|access-date=2015-03-29|archive-date=2014-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817123106/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2011/9789241564373_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mehta|first1=PK|last2=Wei|first2=J|last3=Wenger|first3=NK|title=Ischemic heart disease in women: A focus on risk factors.|journal=Trends in cardiovascular medicine|date=16 October 2014|pmid=25453985}}</ref>。其他的危險因子也包括[[重性憂鬱障礙|憂鬱症]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Charlson|first1=FJ|last2=Moran|first2=AE|last3=Freedman|first3=G|last4=Norman|first4=RE|last5=Stapelberg|first5=NJ|last6=Baxter|first6=AJ|last7=Vos|first7=T|last8=Whiteford|first8=HA|title=The contribution of major depression to the global burden of ischemic heart disease: a comparative risk assessment.|journal=BMC medicine|date=26 November 2013|volume=11|pages=250|pmid=24274053}}</ref>。潛在的病理機制與[[冠狀血管|冠狀動脈血管]]的[[動脈粥樣硬化|粥狀硬化]]有關<ref name=WHO2011/>。[[心電圖|心電圖]]、[[心臟壓力測試|心臟壓力測試]]與{{Link-en|冠狀動脈血管攝影|Coronary catheterization}}是常見有助於診斷的工具<ref>{{cite web |title = How Is Coronary Heart Disease Diagnosed? |url = http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/hecdalth/health-topics/topics/cad/diagnosis |website = http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/ |accessdate = 25 February 2015 |date = September 29, 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

<!--預防與治療-->
預防方式包括：健康飲食、規律運動、體重控制以及戒菸<ref name=HLB2013P>{{cite web |title = How Can Coronary Heart Disease Be Prevented or Delayed? |url = http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/cad/prevention |website = http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/ |accessdate = 25 February 2015 |archive-date = 2015-02-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150224105151/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/cad/prevention |dead-url = no }}</ref>。視情況合併使用藥物控制高血糖、高膽固醇或高血壓<ref name=HLB2013P/>。只有很有限的證據支持對低風險且沒有症狀的民眾實施篩檢<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Desai|first1=CS|last2=Blumenthal|first2=RS|last3=Greenland|first3=P |title=Screening low-risk individuals for coronary artery disease.|journal=Current atherosclerosis reports|date=April 2014|volume=16|issue=4|pages=402|pmid=24522859}}</ref>。最初治療和預防措施一樣，包括生活方式調整以及三高（高血糖、高膽固醇或高血壓）的控制<ref name=HLB2013Tr>{{cite web |title=How Is Coronary Heart Disease Treated? |url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/cad/treatment |website=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/ |accessdate=25 February 2015 |date=September 29, 2014 |archive-date=2015-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224093945/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/cad/treatment |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Boden|first1=WE|last2=Franklin|first2=B|last3=Berra|first3=K|last4=Haskell|first4=WL|last5=Calfas|first5=KJ|last6=Zimmerman |first6=FH|last7=Wenger|first7=NK|title=Exercise as a therapeutic intervention in patients with stable ischemic heart disease: an underfilled prescription.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-medicine_2014-10_127_10/page/905|journal=The American journal of medicine|date=October 2014|volume=127|issue=10|pages=905-11|pmid=24844736}}</ref>。進一步的藥物治療包括[[阿斯匹靈|阿斯匹靈]]、[[乙型交感神經阻斷劑|乙型交感神經阻斷劑]]或[[硝酸甘油|硝酸甘油的醫療用途]]<ref name=HLB2013Tr/>。在病況較嚴重的情形下，會考慮進行[[冠狀動脈再成形術|經皮冠狀動脈介入治療]]或是[[冠狀動脈搭橋手術|冠狀動脈繞道手術]]<ref name=HLB2013Tr/><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Deb|first1=S|last2=Wijeysundera|first2=HC|last3=Ko|first3=DT|last4=Tsubota|first4=H|last5=Hill|first5=S|last6=Fremes|first6=SE|title=Coronary artery bypass graft surgery vs percutaneous interventions in coronary revascularization: a systematic review.|journal=JAMA|date=20 November 2013|volume=310|issue=19|pages=2086-95|pmid=24240936}}</ref>。對於穩定型心絞痛，經皮冠狀動脈介入治療或是冠狀動脈繞道手術，對於提升存活年限或降低未來心臟病發的效果仍不明確<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Rezende|first1=PC|last2=Scudeler|first2=TL|last3=da Costa|first3=LM|last4=Hueb|first4=W|title=Conservative strategy for treatment of stable coronary artery disease.|journal=World journal of clinical cases|date=16 February 2015|volume=3|issue=2|pages=163-70|pmid=25685763}}</ref>。

<!--流行病學 -->
冠狀動脈疾病在西元2002年是[[2002年致死原因及所占比例列表|全球第一大死因]]<ref name=Finegold>{{cite journal |last=Finegold |first=JA |coauthors=Asaria, P; Francis, DP |title=Mortality from ischaemic heart disease by country, region, and age: Statistics from World Health Organisation and United Nations |journal=International journal of cardiology|date=2012-12-04 |pmid=23218570 |doi = 10.1016/j.ijcard.2012.10.046 |volume=168|issue=2|pages=934–45}}</ref>，也是人們住院的主要原因之一<ref name=WHO>{{cite book |author=World Health Organization Department of Health Statistics and Informatics in the Information, Evidence and Research Cluster |title=The global burden of disease 2004 update |publisher=WHO |location=Geneva |year=2004 |isbn=92-4-156371-0}}</ref>。2013年也是全球死因首位，死亡人數自1990年574萬人（12%）攀升至2013年814萬人（16.8%）<ref name=GDB2013/>。而隨著診斷及治療技術進步，經年齡校正後的冠狀動脈疾病死亡率自1980年至2010年則呈現下降趨勢，尤其在[[已開發國家|已開發國家]]更為顯著<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Moran|first1=AE|last2=Forouzanfar|first2=MH|last3=Roth|first3=GA|last4=Mensah|first4=GA|last5=Ezzati|first5=M|last6=Murray |first6=CJ|last7=Naghavi|first7=M|title=Temporal trends in ischemic heart disease mortality in 21 world regions, 1980 to 2010: the Global Burden of Disease 2010 study.|journal=Circulation|date=8 April 2014|volume=129|issue=14|pages=1483-92 |pmid=24573352}}</ref>。同時經年齡校正後的冠狀動脈疾病病例數在1990至2010年間亦呈現下降趨勢<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Moran|first1=AE|last2=Forouzanfar|first2=MH|last3=Roth|first3=GA|last4=Mensah|first4=GA|last5=Ezzati|first5=M|last6=Flaxman|first6=A|last7=Murray|first7=CJ|last8=Naghavi|first8=M|title=The global burden of ischemic heart disease in 1990 and 2010: the Global Burden of Disease 2010 study.|journal=Circulation|date=8 April 2014|volume=129|issue=14|pages=1493-501 |pmid=24573351}}</ref>。根據美國本土於2010年統計，冠狀動脈疾病盛行率於大於65歲族群為20%、45至64歲為7%、18至45歲為1.3%<ref name=US2011>{{cite journal|author = Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) |title=Prevalence of coronary heart disease--United States, 2006-2010. |journal=MMWR. Morbidity and mortality weekly report |date=14 October 2011 |volume=60|issue=40|pages=1377-81 |pmid=21993341}}</ref>。針對同一年齡層相比，男性的發生率較女性高<ref name=US2011/>。

==治疗==
[[冠狀動脈|冠狀動脈]]是主動脈的分支，負責供應足夠氧和營養素予心肌。冠狀動脈被[[膽固醇|膽固醇]]或血凝塊阻塞時，會形成斑塊而引致心臟供血不足，患者需要接受俗稱「通波仔」（粵語打通用的氣球）的[[冠狀動脈再成形術|血管擴張手術]]以氣球擴張冠狀動脈，使之暢通。若冠狀動脈血液被嚴重阻塞，可引致很嚴重的後果。血液不能供應到[[心臟|心臟]]會引致劇烈的'''心絞痛'''，然後心臟會衰竭，最嚴重的可導致[[死亡|死亡]]。當冠心病發作時，須立即口含醫師處方的「[https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%84%B7 脷] {{Wayback|url=https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%84%B7 |date=20220405150340 }}底丸」（粵語舌下丸之義，成分為[[硝酸甘油|硝酸甘油]]），其可扩张血管，以增加冠状动脉血流量。冠心病發作可引致嚴重後果，應立即叫救護車求助。

===健康的生活方式===
*{{link-en|卡德维尔·爱色斯坦|Caldwell Esselstyn}}与[[科林·坎贝尔|科林·坎贝尔]]证明，[[素食|素食]]对改善冠心病和[[动脉硬化|动脉硬化]]有很大效果。他们的同事也从许多研究中确认，素食使得许多患者的病情得以停止发展，甚至出现好转。<ref name="Prevent and Reverse Heart Disease">{{Cite web |url=http://www.heartattackproof.com/resolving_cade.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106233111/http://www.heartattackproof.com/resolving_cade.htm |archive-date=2012-01-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>Preventive Cardiology; 2001; 4: p171-177</ref>此类建议（增加素食，减少荤菜）已经在至少50年前就被提出了。<ref>morrison l m "diet in coronary artherosclerosis" JAMA 173; 1960; p884-888</ref><ref name="mayoclinic.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/coronary-artery-disease/DS00064/DSECTION=treatments%2Dand%2Ddrugs |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-31 |archive-date=2013-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219232545/http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/coronary-artery-disease/DS00064/DSECTION=treatments-and-drugs |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*控制体重
*停止吸烟、酗酒
*锻炼
*适量的鱼油（尤其是海鱼，如[[鮪魚|金枪鱼]]、[[鮭魚|三文鱼]]）摄入，以补充[[ω−3脂肪酸|ω−3脂肪酸]]<ref name="NLM">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/druginfo/natural/993.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-31 |archive-date=2015-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705225237/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/druginfo/natural/993.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
